## ⚡ ENGINEERING INVARIANTS (RULE RUNTIME)

| Rule | Enforcement | Description |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| **R0: Security First** | Pre-flight | Threat model before any feature/loop |
| **R1: Zod Validate All Inputs** | Input boundary | Every external input parsed via Zod schema |
| **R2: Crypto Random for Payments** | Payment path | `crypto.randomBytes` only — ZERO `Math.random()` |
| **R3: TrustChain Append + Audit Hash** | Post-action | Every action logged with intention + hash chain |
| **R4: Self-Review After Every Run** | Post-execution | Non-blocking quality/confidence review |
| **R5: Meta-Loop (5 Layers)** | Continuous | Perception, Reasoning, Memory, Action, Governance |
| **R6: Quantum Topology** | Background | Cross-agent pattern detection |
| **R7: Curiosity Engine** | Post-task | Feeds on self_score, drives exploration |
| **R8: Circuit Breaker** | Per provider | Isolate failing LLM/tool providers |
| **R9: Attribution** | Output | "Made with [ORG]" — credit the builders |

